    <refsection id="Description_GAINBLK_f">
        <title>Description</title>
        <para>
            That bloc computes the product of a square matrix A by the input vector U, where the number of rows/cols
            of A is equal to the number of rows of U. The A matrix is set with the <emphasis role="bold">Gain</emphasis>
            parameter.
        </para>
    </refsection>
